(45, '[{\"row\":{\"column\":[{\"cells\":[{\"editorName\":\"text-editor\",\"editorContent\":\"<p>The two functions <span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">getContent()</span> and <span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">setContentEditor(contentEditor)</span> are required for working with the <em>page-O-builder</em>, as described in <a href=\\\"https://page-o-builder.frissbee.de/docs/implementation\\\" title=\\\"https://page-o-builder.frissbee.de/docs/implementation\\\" target=\\\"_self\\\">Implementation</a>.</p><p>If you want to integrate the <em>page-O-builder</em> into your own project, you can also use the following functions.</p><p><br></p><p style=\\\"font-size: 18.4px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bolder; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\\\">setNewPage()</span></p><p style=\\\"font-size: 18.4px;\\\">Removes the content of the&nbsp;<em>page-O-builder</em>&nbsp;that was set with&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\\\">setContentEditor()</span>&nbsp;and sets the&nbsp;<em>page-O-builder</em>&nbsp;to \\\"New Page\\\".</p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\\\">setEditPage()</strong></p><p>Sets the display of the <em>page-O-builder</em> from \\\"preview\\\" to \\\"edit\\\".</p><p>Example for set the page-O-builder to \\\"New Page\\\":</p><pre class=\\\"language-js\\\" data-line=\\\"1-4\\\"><code class=\\\"language-js\\\"><span class=\\\"token keyword\\\">const</span> pageBuilder <span class=\\\"token operator\\\">=</span> document<span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">.</span><span class=\\\"token function\\\">querySelector</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">(</span><span class=\\\"token string\\\">\'page-o-builder\'</span><span class=\\\"token punctuation\\\">)</span><span class=\\\"tok