 color</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The background color for the cell can be defined here. To remove this again, you can use the \"transparent\" button.</span></p><p><strong>8. background image</strong></p><p>The link (URL) to a background image for the cell can be entered here.</p><p><strong>9. padding</strong></p><p style=\"font-size: 18.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">With padding you can define the inner spacing in pixels.</p><p style=\"font-size: 18.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The order is: top right bottom left</p><p style=\"font-size: 18.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Examples:</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">25px 50px 75px 100px</span><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">top padding is 25px</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">right padding is 50px</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">bottom padding is 75px</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">left padding is 100px</li></ul></li></ul><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">25px 50px 75px</span><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">top padding is 25px</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">right and left paddings are 50px</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">bottom padding is 75px</li></ul></li></ul><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">25px 50p</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">x</span><ul sty